data.description: Photos coming soonThis immaculate and well-maintained home is now available for you to call your own. Nestled in Westbrooke subdivision, this property offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious inviting light area with abundant natural light flowing through the large windows. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen which is great for entertaining.Enjoy your private retreat in the well maintained backyard, offering plenty of space for gardening, playtime, or simply unwinding after a long day.Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this charming home in a sought-after location.
